  The reason they scare me is because they have amazing buffs, decent armor class, decent hitpoints, nice dots, mind numbing slows, and the malise line.  Ever had your poison and disease resists reduced to negatives? it's very uncool. Don't forget the pet interrupting your pumice.<br>
  They might not be able to kill you as fast as a wizard could, but i can assure you that you will die eventually without some luck if jumped by a decent shaman, unless you carry a backpack full of cure poison and disease potions..<br>
----------<br>
